data.description: ***Price Improvement*** One owner home. This beautiful home offers an open floor plan with vaulted ceilings, perfect for entertaining. The main floor features a family room with a cozy fireplace - plantation shutters - wired for surround sound - add'l electrical for hookups, chef gourmet kitchen with buffet bar - new appliances - granite countertops - new backsplash - plantation shutters - windowsill tiled - easy access to outdoor entertaining on the large gorgeous covered deck (43' X 16'2") Yes you read that correct - this deck can also access the upper sundeck (16'4" X 9'6") - beautifully landscaped backyard, formal living room with vaulted ceilings and new custom paint, formal dining room with new custom paint, a bedroom with a walk-in closet, full bathroom with new flooring and vanity, and laundry room including utility sink - cabinets & shelving. The upstairs features a private primary bedroom with a 5 piece en-suite - new faucets and sinks - new wood laminate flooring - flex room with door to sundeck (16'4" X 9'6") - and a huge walk-in closet (11' X 11'5") with added lower shelving, bedroom adjoins with a full bath, plus three additional bedrooms, loft/flex space, full bathroom with new sinks & faucets - new wood laminate flooring - safety bar installed in shower/tub. The basement is ready for you to make it your own - includes bathroom rough-in - two radon mitigation systems. This home includes a whole house humidifier and air purifier. The exterior includes mature landscaping - covered front patio - decks for outdoor living - garden area - and the exterior of the home was painted in 2019. Three car garage with forced gas heater - garage doors serviced 09/2023 - service door to backyard - shelving for storage. New roof & gutters 2019. Close to Schools - Shopping - Dining - DIA - Denver. This home is absolutely beautiful and a must see!
